      <DOI>https://doi.org/10.24400/802406/h6zn-txn0</DOI>
      <ReleaseDate>2022-03-14T12:16:41Z</ReleaseDate>
      <Description>This dataset contains measurements of the magnetic field Calibrated WaveForm from the STAFF-SC instrument in NBR mode (filtered from 0.6 Hz to 10Hz and sampled at 25 Hz) and in HBR mode (filtered from 0.6 Hz to 180Hz and sampled at 450 Hz) on the Cluster C4 spacecraft.

This product is given in the GSE frame.

Data calibration is performed using a moving window of 1024 points in NBR mode and 4096 points in HBR mode.

These values were chosen as the best compromise for routine production.</Description>
